{"tid":494394,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[找數] (極醜惡Boardgame第二回) 千億探長之出得嚟行預左要還","createTime":"2017-12-09T14:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T18:26:53.000Z","uid":43487,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d9b277290bcfc985337bf80dfe0a4f66e332184b","tid":494394,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:39:06.000Z","msg":"上回提要:(<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/481214/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/481214/page/1</a>)<br />\n<br />\n上次我地POST左隻GAME同整左個抽獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5s6jmcX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5s6jmcX.jpg&h=3c175291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝各位巴絲熱烈支持, 呢兩個禮拜我地都陸續約到人出嚟試GAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根據正評數, 我地而家總共送出10隻GAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為技術問題，所以條抽獎片等到而家先拍到,SORRY<br />\n片:<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YXWS6AtUsRc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYXWS6AtUsRc&d=I9q57khBnM14iE4uKaveFsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e0199c58\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YXWS6AtUsRc</a><br />\n<br />\n條片其實只係想證明我地真係有抽到, 重點都係得獎名單<br />\n得獎者如下：<br />\n<br />\nBomdia #60643<br />\nDMM_AV破解員 #24534<br />\n串過碼頭姑喱 #33673<br />\n切啫琢磨 #52032<br />\n吾你老母咩 #20422<br />\n桂小太郎 #36820<br />\n歷膏 #38044<br />\n殊頭同龜 #7382<br />\n老鼠夾 #20312<br />\n銀灰色的死 #31827<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抽中左嘅巴絲請fb pm番我地/TG搵我地約時間拎game<br />\nFB:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/headblownstudio/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fheadblownstudio%2F&d=I9q57khBnM14iE4uKaveFsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=7cfdb242\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/headblownstudio/</a><br />\nTG:<a href=\"https://t.me/issssacliu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fissssacliu&d=I9q57khBnM14iE4uKaveFsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=de68deaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/issssacliu</a><br />\n<br />\n抽唔中嘅巴絲唔洗失望，我地嚟緊都會喺fb每個星期搞多次giveaway<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n詳情記住like 我地fb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbd0634a86e0b457d0df56873e6619d800bfa6f","tid":494394,"uid":43487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"想試GAME隨時歡迎聯絡我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便POST下血汗工廠整PROTOTYPE嘅相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/02/201114_fad02581567c1396a679c486e0a85c49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F201114_fad02581567c1396a679c486e0a85c49.jpg&h=7297c507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/221326_7a257ecc05824be95b65b886eb1a48ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F221326_7a257ecc05824be95b65b886eb1a48ed.jpg&h=e7f47032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCUT完大概係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/02/003246_f85aee0d25db0fa1a3300c3388e98e64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F003246_f85aee0d25db0fa1a3300c3388e98e64.jpg&h=8af98de0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97f56f5c111a3b94eac3667c712c0cf0ec5aaa37","tid":494394,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a1543a3635bee9b9e410db9e938f8a75795755","tid":494394,"uid":17733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:32:33.000Z","msg":"支持<img sr